title: 820-02098 no power
message:
This arrived with no power and no visible signs of liquid damage. PP3V8_AON was slightly shorted at 0.172 diode and 0v on arrival. Q5800 was causing the short. Replaced Q5800/Q5820/Q5840 and U7500.

Short is gone however PP3V8_AON is only 1.4V now. Under thermal camera something around Q5800 is getting hot however I have already replaced Q5800 twice.

What should be checked next?
